@startuml
actor User
participant Frontend
participant Backend
database DB

User -> Frontend: Apre area riservata
Frontend -> Backend: GET /Backend/v1/bookings/me
Backend -> DB: Recupera prenotazioni utente
DB --> Backend: Lista prenotazioni
Backend --> Frontend: 200 OK { bookings }
Frontend -> Backend: GET /Backend/v1/reports/me
Backend -> DB: Recupera referti dell'utente
DB --> Backend: Lista referti
Backend --> Frontend: 200 OK { reports }
User -> Frontend: Clicca su "Scarica" su un referto
Frontend -> Backend: GET /Backend/v1/reports/{id}/download
Backend -> DB: Verifica permessi utente
DB --> Backend: OK
Backend --> Frontend: file PDF
Frontend -> User: Scarica file
@enduml